      <title>法兰克福天际线因旧办公楼空置而变暗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/frankfurt-s-skyline-darkens-as-old-office-buildings-sit-vacant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在法兰克福最中心的街区之一，距离城市主要火车站只有几步之遥，一栋 19 层的高楼曾是德国中央合作银行联合投资部门的办公场所，现已空置四年多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/frankfurt-s-skyline-darkens-as-old-office-buildings-sit-vacant</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
